# Project Setup Guide

## Technologies Used
- Astro framework with React integration
- React v19
- TailwindCSS v4
- Shadcn UI

## Development Environment
- Package manager: Bun
- Run commands with Bun
- For binary commands use: `bunx --bun [command]`
- Add shadcn components using: `bunx --bun shadcn@latest add [component]`

## Getting Started
```sh
# Install dependencies
bun install

# Start development server
bun run dev
```
